data.description: ''Welcome to this enchanting Key West-style cottage exuding charm and character! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this delightful two-bedroom, one-bathroom home boasts a picturesque setting and inviting curb appeal.Step inside to discover the warmth of hardwood floors that lead you through the cozy living spaces highlighted by a decorative fireplace, adding a touch of elegance and comfort. The ambiance is further accentuated by the abundance of natural light streaming in through the classic French doors.The allure continues outdoors, where the generous yard beckons with ample space for entertaining and relaxing. Imagine hosting gatherings or enjoying tranquil evenings in this idyllic setting.
